column6: description:{"en":"(from amazon.jp):\n\nThis is a collection of 11 short manga by Katsuhiro Otomo
column7: who was 17-19 years old and still a minor
column9: from the period when he was a student contributor to his professional debut.\n\nThe mangaka made his official debut at the age of just 19 with \"Gunshot\" in the August 4 supplementary issue of Weekly Manga Action in 1973
column10: and none of his first seven short stories have been published in any previous tankoban. They are literally \"phantom early works\".\n\nThis compilation includes all of these works for the first time
column11: as well as four completely unpublished manga
column12: which were studies and submissions made before the Otomo's debut.\n\nIt is a miracle that the originals of these works still exist
column13: but the mangaka's permission to include these unpublished works was also a special measure taken for the \"complete works\" project
column14: and the realization of this release is truly a \"once in a half-century\" miracle.\n\nIt is up to the reader to decide whether to dismiss it as a collection of crude
column16: immature works or to be horrified by the expression of a \"terrible child\" with fresh sensibility and a maturity that is hard to believe for a teenage boy. \n\nThe value of this tankoban is immeasurable as a \"one-of-a-kind record\" that shows the moment when a creator who would later make a name for himself in the world was born
column17: as well as the moments before and after.\n\nOnly 10 years after his debut
column19: the still unknown \"monster\" began to make \"AKIRA\". Finally! It is now being brought back to life!\n\n\"OTOMO THE COMPLETE WORKS\" Volume 1"}

ja:"ここは異世界？
いいえ、現代日本です！

突如、世界各地に『ダンジョン』が現れて４年。
世界ではその内に眠る資源を巡り利権争いが勃発していた。

そんなある日――
ど田舎に左遷された社畜証券マンの水樹が目にしたのは今まさに『ダンジョン』と化した職場の成れの果てだった。

巻き込まれた人がいないか捜索するべく踏み込んだそこはゲームのダンジョンそのもの！

そして、妖精・ケシーがゴブリンに丸焼きにされそうな所を間一髪、手に入れた謎スキル『スキルブック』で救出に成功。
無事にダンジョンからの脱出を果たす。

ところが、偶然GETした謎スキルとお喋り妖精はとんでもないシロモノだったようで――!?

現代にあらわれたダンジョンを舞台に、『スキルブック』を片手に異世界の相棒と挑む元社畜サラリーマンの冒険ファンタジー、開幕！"}
